          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated value based on data from United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (comtrade.un.org). UN comtrade category:  170199 Refined sugar, in solid form, nes, pure sucrose. Year 2005. Using exchange rate of 1EURO = 1.209 USD. Average of price of import into 5 main markets (EU, US, JP, IN and CN). The price of raw sugar, from sugarbeet calcualted using the values from the comtrade database is 0.71 EUR/kg, but there are not many values available so the resulting number has very high uncertainty.</comment>
